reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Careful! Bad product.
reviews.reviewText: The screen protectors are bad quality. The application device does not align properly and there is enough space between it and the phone so it just doesn’t work. The glass applies with a bunch of big and tiny bubbles that do not come off. Two different people applied two different protectors on two different phones just to make sure it was the product and not us.The pack does not come with a squeegee so it’s up to you to find something to try to push the bubbles away (without it working anyway).It only comes with one alignment device so the screen protectors are not pre applied so that probably doesn’t help (you have to put them on yourself).Overall terrible product. Do not buy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great screen protector but don’t put a tight case on it.
reviews.reviewText: This temperglass is really good. The entire glass spreads ALL the way to the edge of the screen. You wouldn’t even know it was there if you put it on correctly. The only downside is, I bought 2 otterbox cases. The Otterbox symmetry series case fit perfectly over and I only saw tiny bubbles along the edge. You would only notice if you looked really close while the screen is turned off. But then I got a Otterbox Defender XT case. And when I put that on it lifted the ENTIRE temper glass. And when you try to push it underneath you’re left with a HUGE, noticeable bubble along the lower half of the screen. I’m disappointed. Cause I love the defender case but that means I would have to look for another temper glass that has a little more space between the glass and the actual case. But the screen protector is really good.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: We purchased two sets of these (one for our iPhone 15 and one for our IPhone 15 pro - yes you need to purchase one for each specific phone even tho the screen size is same their is a slight difference). They were SOO EASY to install. Now we did get a couple of small little bubble clusters when we were installing but we didn’t panic - all we did was kept using the dry cleaning cloth (which is included) and applied pressure as we wiped the bubbles towards the edges until they disappeared AND they turned out PERFECT!! Great price and it’s sooo easy to use !!!
